This isn&#8217;t the first time that residents of La Mesa have been terrorised by criminals.Over the years there have been many incidents particularly in La Mesa and La Junta in Johannesburg.Last year a resident was held up while waiting for her friend outside.An intruder was caught on CCTV on 6 December while inspecting the security measures before he tried to gain entry into the complex.Residents claim that criminals were using the section of the park to hide and attack them. Criminals have attacked several people from our complexes. It is like we are living in a war zone, said one of the residents, Mike GowerIn the video below we see a women being terrorised by two criminals with a punga. It would be nice if something was done about the rampant criminality in our country.&nbsp;